\par Hasra v\'e1gtuk magunkat.
\par }\pard \qj \fi284\li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4079637 \cbpat8 {\fs24\cf1\insrsid4079637\charrsid8070642 A f\'e9men \'e1tk\'fcld\'f6tt goly\'f3k els\'fcv\'edtettek f\'f6l\'f6tt\'fcnk.
